OL,3,CNumber of homeless people in England
OL,4,Con given day this year 14% higher than
OL,5,C2023
OL,7,FThe number of homeless people in
OL,8,FEngland on a given night this year is
OL,9,F14% higher than 2023, new research
OL,10,Ffrom Shelter has suggested.
OL,12,FAround one in 160 people were
OL,13,Festimated to be homeless in England on
OL,14,Fa given night in 2024.
OL,16,FThe charity said its research into
OL,17,Fpeople living in temporary
OL,18,Faccommodation, sleeping on the streets
OL,19,Fand living in hostels is "the most
OL,20,Fcomprehensive overview of recorded
OL,21,Fhomelessness in England".
