OL,7,FShelter chief executive Polly Neate
OL,8,Fsaid: "As the country prepares to wind
OL,9,Fdown and celebrate the festive season
OL,10,Fin our homes, it's unimaginable that
OL,11,F354,000 will spend this winter
OL,12,Fhomeless ` many of them forced to
OL,13,Fshiver on the wet streets or in a
OL,14,Fmouldy hostel room with their entire
OL,15,Ffamily.
OL,17,F"Across England, extortionate private
OL,18,Frents combined with a dire lack of
OL,19,Fgenuinely affordable social homes is
OL,20,Ftrapping more and more people in
OL,21,Fhomelessness.
